name: Together as One!
description: Elite Shout. For 3...13...15 seconds, all party members near you or near your pet deal +5...13...15 additional damage with attacks and gain +1...6...7 Health regeneration. PvE Skill

name: Antidote Signet
description: Signet. Cleanse yourself of Poison, Disease, and Blindness, and one additional condition.

name: Apply Poison
description: Preparation. For 24 seconds, foes struck by your physical attacks become Poisoned for 3...13...15 seconds.

name: Barbed Trap
description: Trap. When Barbed Trap is triggered, all nearby foes are struck for 7...20...23 piercing damage, become Crippled, and begin Bleeding for 3...21...25 seconds.  Barbed Trap ends after 90 seconds.  While activating this skill, you are easily interrupted.

name: Barrage
description: Elite Bow Attack. All your preparations are removed. Shoot arrows at target foe and up to 5 foes adjacent to your target. These arrows strike for +5...17...20 damage if they hit.

name: Call of Haste
description: Shout.  For 30 seconds, your animal companion has a 33% faster attack speed and moves 33% faster.

name: Call of Haste (PvP)
description: Shout.  For 30 seconds, your animal companion has a 25% faster attack speed and moves 25% faster.

name: Called Shot
description: Bow Attack. Shoot an arrow that moves 3 times faster and cannot be blocked.

name: Charm Animal
description: Skill. Charm target animal. Once charmed, your animal companion will travel with you whenever you have Charm Animal equipped. You cannot charm an animal that is more than 4 levels above you.

name: Charm Animal (Codex)
description: Skill. Your animal companion will travel with you whenever you have Charm Animal equipped and have at least 8 points in Beast Mastery.

name: Choking Gas
description: Preparation. For 1...10...12 seconds, your arrows deal 1...7...8 more damage and spread Choking Gas to all adjacent foes on impact.  Choking Gas interrupts foes attempting to cast spells.

name: Comfort Animal
description: Skill.  You heal your animal companion for 20...87...104 Health. If your companion is dead, it is resurrected with 10...48...58% Health. If you have Comfort Animal equipped, your animal companion will travel with you.

name: Comfort Animal (PvP)
description: Skill. You heal your animal companion for 20...87...104 Health. If your companion is dead, it is resurrected with 10...48...58% Health.

name: Concussion Shot
description: Bow Attack. If Concussion Shot hits while target foe is casting a spell, the spell is interrupted and your target is Dazed for 5...17...20 seconds.  This attack deals only 1...13...16 damage.

name: Debilitating Shot
description: Bow Attack. If Debilitating Shot hits, your target loses 1...8...10 Energy.

name: Determined Shot
description: Bow Attack. If Determined Shot hits, you strike for +5...17...20 damage. If Determined Shot fails to hit, all of your attack skills are recharged.

name: Disrupting Lunge
description: Pet Attack. Your animal companion attempts a Disrupting Lunge that deals +1...10...12 damage. If that attack strikes a foe using a skill that skill is interrupted and is disabled for an additional 20 seconds.

name: Distracting Shot
description: Bow Attack. If Distracting Shot hits, it interrupts target foe's action but deals only 1...13...16 damage. If the interrupted action was a skill, that skill is disabled for an additional 20 seconds.

name: Dual Shot
description: Bow Attack. Shoot two arrows simultaneously at target foe.  These arrows deal 25% less damage.

name: Energizing Wind
description: Nature Ritual. Create a level 1...5...6 spirit. For non-spirit creatures within its range, all skills cost 15 less Energy (minimum cost 10 Energy), and skills recharge 25% slower. This spirit dies after 1...25...31 second[s].

name: Escape
description: Elite Stance. For 1...7...8 second[s], you move 33% faster and have a 75% chance to block attacks.

name: Escape (PvP)
description: Elite Stance. For 1...7...8 second[s], you move 33% faster and have a 75% chance to block attacks. Escape ends if you make a melee attack.

name: Favorable Winds
description: Nature Ritual. Create a level 1...8...10 spirit.  For non-spirit creatures within its range, arrows move twice as fast and strike for +6 damage.  This spirit dies after 30...126...150 seconds.

name: Ferocious Strike
description: Elite Pet Attack. Your animal companion attempts a Ferocious Strike that deals  +13...25...28 damage. If that attack hits, you gain adrenaline and 3...9...10 Energy.

name: Flame Trap
description: Trap. When Flame Trap is triggered, every second (for 3 seconds total), all nearby foes are struck for 5...17...20 fire damage and set on fire for 1...3...3 second[s]. Flame Trap ends after 90 seconds. While activating this skill, you are easily interrupted.

name: Hunter's Shot
description: Bow Attack. If this attack hits, your target bleeds for 3...21...25 seconds.

name: Kindle Arrows
description: Preparation. For 24 seconds, your arrows deal fire damage and hit for an additional 3...20...24 fire damage.

name: Lightning Reflexes
description: Stance. For 5...10...11 seconds, you have a 75% chance to block melee and projectile attacks, and you attack 33% faster.

name: Lightning Reflexes (PvP)
description: Stance. For 5...10...11 seconds, you have a 75% chance to block melee and projectile attacks, and you attack 33% faster.

name: Maiming Strike
description: Pet Attack. Your animal companion attempts a Maiming Strike that deals +5...17...20 damage. If that attack hits a moving foe that foe becomes Crippled for 3...13...15 seconds.

name: Nature's Renewal
description: Nature Ritual. Create a level 1...8...10 spirit. For 30...126...150 seconds, enchantments and hexes cast by non-spirit creatures in range take twice as long to cast, and it costs twice as much Energy to maintain enchantments. This spirit dies after 30...126...150 seconds.

name: Pin Down
description: Bow Attack. If Pin Down hits, your target is Crippled for 3...13...15 seconds.

name: Power Shot
description: Bow Attack. If Power Shot hits, target foe takes 25...45...50 damage.

name: Precision Shot
description: Bow Attack. If Precision Shot hits, you strike for +3...9...10 damage. Precision Shot cannot be blocked. This action is easily interrupted.

name: Primal Echoes
description: Nature Ritual. Create a level 1...8...10 Spirit. For non-Spirit creatures within its range, Signets cost 10 Energy to use. This Spirit dies after 30...126...150 seconds.

name: Quick Shot
description: Elite Bow Attack. Shoot an arrow that moves twice as fast.

name: Quickening Zephyr
description: Nature Ritual. Create a level 1...8...10 spirit. For non-spirit creatures within its range, all skills recharge twice as fast and cost 30% more of the base Energy to cast. This spirit dies after 15...39...45 seconds.

name: Read the Wind
description: Preparation. For 24 seconds, your arrows move twice as fast and deal 3...9...10 extra damage.

name: Read the Wind (PvP)
description: Preparation. For 24 seconds, your arrows move twice as fast.

name: Savage Shot
description: Bow Attack. If Savage Shot hits, your target's action is interrupted.  If that action was a spell, you strike for +13...25...28 damage.

name: Scavenger Strike
description: Pet Attack. Your animal companion attempts a Scavenger Strike that deals +10...22...25 damage. If the attack strikes a foe who is suffering a condition, you gain 3...13...15 Energy.

name: Spike Trap
description: Elite Trap. When Spike Trap is triggered, every second (for 2 seconds), all nearby foes are struck for 10...34...40 piercing damage, become Crippled for 3...21...25 seconds, and are knocked down. Spike Trap ends after 90 seconds. While activating this skill, you are easily interrupted.

name: Storm Chaser
description: Stance. For 8...18...20 seconds, you move 25% faster, and you gain 1...4...5 Energy whenever you take elemental damage.

name: Throw Dirt
description: Skill. Target touched foe and foes adjacent to your target become Blinded for 3...13...15 seconds.

name: Troll Unguent
description: Skill. For 13 seconds, you gain +3...9...10 Health regeneration.

name: Whirling Defense
description: Stance. For 8...18...20 seconds, you have 75% chance to block attacks. Whenever you block a projectile in this way, adjacent foes take 5...10...11 damage.

name: Winnowing
description: Nature Ritual. Create a level 1...8...10 spirit.  Non-spirit creatures within range take 4 additional damage whenever they take physical damage.  This spirit dies after 30...126...150 seconds.
